content: Convenient analyzing of the collected responses

comment.text: This translation key describes a header used in a dialog that provides analyzing capabilities of collected responses. The header is intended to be displayed as part of a form-filling tips dialog, guiding users on how to analyze their responses.

ai_spell_check_issues.description: The translation 'Βολική ανάλυση των απαντήσεων που συλλέγονται' is somewhat literal and could be improved for flow and naturalness in Greek. While technically correct, it doesn't convey the 'convenient' aspect as smoothly as other options.

The translation 'Kätevä kerättyjen vastausten analysointi' is not a precise equivalent of 'Convenient analyzing of the collected responses'. While 'kerättyjen vastausten analysointi' accurately translates 'analyzing of the collected responses', 'Kätevä' (convenient) is a bit clunky. A more natural Finnish phrasing would be needed to capture the nuance of 'convenient'.
ai_spell_check_issues.suggestion: Consider 'Helppo kerättyjen vastausten analysointi' or 'Vaivaton kerättyjen vastausten analysointi' for a more natural and accurate translation of 'Convenient analyzing of the collected responses'.

ai_spell_check_issues.description: The English phrase 'Convenient analyzing' implies ease and efficiency. 'Pratica' in Italian translates to 'practical' or 'hands-on,' which doesn't fully convey the meaning of 'convenient'. While not incorrect, it's a less ideal translation.
ai_spell_check_issues.suggestion: Consider a translation that emphasizes convenience, such as 'Analisi agevole delle risposte raccolte' or 'Analisi semplice delle risposte raccolte'.

ai_spell_check_issues.description: The translation "수집된 응답 간단 분석" doesn't fully capture the meaning of "Convenient analyzing of the collected responses." The word 'convenient' is missing, and the phrasing is a bit abrupt.
ai_spell_check_issues.suggestion: 수집된 응답의 간편한 분석 (Sujipdoen ungdabeun-ui ganpyeonhan bunseok)

ai_spell_check_issues.description: The sentence could benefit from a more natural flow in Korean.  The current translation is quite direct and sounds slightly robotic.
ai_spell_check_issues.suggestion: 수집된 응답을 간편하게 분석할 수 있습니다. (Sujipdoen ungdabeun-eul ganpyeonhage bunseokhal su issseumnida)

ai_spell_check_issues.description: The English phrase "Convenient analyzing of the collected responses" implies ease and efficiency in analyzing the data. The Lao translation "ການວິເຄາະຜົນການຕອບສະແດງທີ່ເຕົ້າໂຮມໄວ້ຢ່າງສະດວກສະບາຍ" while technically correct, doesn't quite capture the same sense of convenience and ease. "ທີ່ເຕົ້າໂຮມໄວ້" (that are collected) makes it slightly more formal than the original.
ai_spell_check_issues.suggestion: ການວິເຄາະຜົນການຕອບສະແດງທີ່ເຕົ້າໂຮມໄວ້ຢ່າງງ່າຍດາຍ

ai_spell_check_issues.description: The English phrase 'Convenient analyzing' doesn't directly translate to 'Análise cómoda'. 'Convenient' implies ease of use or efficiency, which 'cómoda' (comfortable) doesn't necessarily convey. A better translation would focus on the ease or efficiency of the analysis.

The translation 'එකතු කරන ලද ප්‍රතිචාර විශ්ලේෂණය කිරීම පහසුයි.' is a literal translation and doesn't fully capture the meaning of 'Convenient analyzing of the collected responses'. It sounds somewhat formal and less natural in Sinhala. A more natural phrasing would emphasize ease or simplicity.
ai_spell_check_issues.suggestion: Consider a translation like 'එකතු කරන ප්‍රතිචාර විශ්ලේෂණය කිරීම සරලයි.' (Collecting and analyzing responses is simple.) or 'එකතු කරන ලද ප්‍රතිචාර විශ්ලේෂණය කිරීමේ පහසුවක්.' (The convenience of analyzing collected responses).

ai_spell_check_issues.description: The translation 'Лако анализирање прикупљених одговора' does not accurately convey the meaning of 'Convenient analyzing of the collected responses'. 'Лако' translates to 'easily' or 'lightly', which doesn't capture the meaning of 'convenient'.

The translation 'Lako analiziranje prikupljenih odgovora' while understandable, isn't the most natural or precise translation of 'Convenient analyzing of the collected responses'. 'Lako' implies ease, but 'convenient' encompasses more functionality and efficiency.
ai_spell_check_issues.suggestion: Pogodnije bi bilo: 'Praktičan/Efikasan pregled prikupljenih odgovora' or 'Udoban/Jednostavan pregled prikupljenih odgovora', depending on the nuance desired.

ai_spell_check_issues.description: The translation 'Phân tích thuận tiện các câu trả lời thu thập được' is a literal translation but sounds awkward in Vietnamese. 'Thuận tiện' (convenient) is not the most natural word choice here.
ai_spell_check_issues.suggestion: Phân tích dễ dàng các câu trả lời đã thu thập

ai_spell_check_issues.description: While grammatically correct, 'các câu trả lời đã thu thập' can be simplified for better flow.

The English phrase 'Convenient analyzing of the collected responses' implies ease and efficiency in analyzing the data. While '方便分析收集到的回答' is technically correct, it doesn't fully capture the 'convenient' aspect. '方便' focuses solely on ease, while the original emphasizes both ease and functionality.
ai_spell_check_issues.suggestion: 便捷地分析收集到的回答
